channel.title: [PI] Webclient - Cache won't download
channel.description:
I know this has been posted many times, and I have read them all..
When I try to make Webclient, it says ''unable to download cache'' in client. Client works fine normally (as desktop client) and auto downloads cache..
Ric's webclient tutorial or posts on mopar haven't helped me out.. any suggestions what do I need to do?
